* Auto Results: Clears, recalculates, and uploads results to RaceRoster.
*   When to use:    During or after the race to prepare and publish results.
*   How to use:     Double-click for a one-time run.
*   Auto-run:       Right-click and select "Auto run" to repeat at a timed interval.
*   Setup:          Set your RaceRoster sub-event ID in Entries.INI (%rr_5k%).

* Step 1: Clear and recalculate all result fields
@CalcPlaces.lst

* Step 2: Upload results to RaceRoster
@ResultsToRR.lst